data.description: An Exceptional Home Close to Disney and a Renowned Golf Resort. Discover this exceptional home situated in close proximity to the Disney area and a renowned golf resort. This fully renovated house perfect for AIRBNB with great bookings performance or full time residence boasts a recently installed roof with architectural shingles, backed by a 28-year warranty. Nestled within a beautiful, gated, and serene community, the property features a pool that overlooks a picturesque reservation area. The exterior of the house has received a complete makeover, with fresh paint adorning both the house and the driveway. Experience the epitome of comfort, style, and convenience in this remarkable home, ideally located near Disney and a world-class golf resort.
